name: Pi*r²
description:
Generative art created with native JS and Canvas. 
Click to change animation.
Hold the "N + F + T" keys to change fill/stroke mode.
Press space to change color mode.
Press left/right arrow to change line width.
I recommend watching in full screen mode.
